I"Î<p>This is not a smoothed LDA. The model is <a href="http://www.jmlr.org/papers/volume3/blei03a/blei03a.pdf">Beli, Ng, and Jordan (2003)</a> Figure 1.<br />
You can find another useful derivation <a href="http://chasen.org/~daiti-m/paper/lda-fullvb.pdf">note</a>.</p>

